    "[0: 57-1:17] In the scenario demonstration, Palantir notes that using their system effectively requires a deep understanding of \"military doctrine, logistics and battle dynamics\" [5:51-5:55].",
    "Implicit is the notion that doctrine contains the legal and ethical values required to ensure human responsibility over decisions.",
